casebody.data:
Miscellaneous Orders.

No. 482. Seatrain Lines, Inc. v. West India Fruit & Steamship Co., Inc. et al. Arthur L. Winn, Jr. for petitioner. William Radner, Odell Kominers, Frank J. McConnell, Joseph M. Rault and Arthur M. Boal for the West India Fruit & S. S. Co.; Joseph Walker for Loftin et al., Trustees; and S. Stanley Kreutser for McCauley, respondents.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit dismissed on motion of counsel for the petitioner.
